CPU:   Temperature 38 C, calibration data: 0x58c00000
DBG snvs regs(addr, data and info): 0x8f8010, 0x179c1183, 0x70000
Reset cause: unknown reset
Board: MX6SX SABRE SDB
I2C:   ready
DRAM:  1 GiB
